item.title: You Won't Believe What Happens When You Try This At-Home Trick to Whiten Fillings on Your Teeth!
item.description: Introduction Do you have fillings on your teeth that are discolored or stained? Have you been looking for a way to whiten them, but don’t want to pay for expensive dental treatments? If so, you’re in luck! There is a simple at-home trick that you can use to whiten your fillings, and the results are amazing! Overview of the At-Home Trick to Whiten Fillings on Teeth This at-home trick to whiten fillings on teeth is surprisingly simple.
